  "article": "In a significant development for the gaming industry, AMD has announced that the highly anticipated Crimson Desert will be the second game to support its FidelityFX Super Resolution (FSR) upscaling technology. This news comes on the heels of the recent launch of FSR, which has been widely praised as a viable open-source alternative to NVIDIA's proprietary DLSS solution.

