  "seo_title": "Caitríona Balfe Bids Farewell to 'Outlander' as Series Ends",
  "meta_description": "Caitríona Balfe, the star of 'Outlander', opens up about saying goodbye to the show, her final day on set, and the lasting legacy of Claire and Jamie's story.",
